    "body": "This PR is required for tuning models with fp8 block quantization (e.g. DeepSeekV3).\nThe current implementation of fp8 tuning does not take into account the block quantization and hence, when tuning DSv3, it does not factor in the weight scales. This PR adds this support.\n- (Along with condition to check config divisibility by block quant shape)",
